vote.title: Adoption of a resolution appointing Kimberly Bizor Tolbert as Interim City Manager, effective at the close of business on May 2, 2024, to serve until the City Council selects and appoints the City Manager - Financing: This action has no cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information)
